<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>TrimWise</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #040814;
      color: #f8fafc;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .features {
      text-align: left;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .features li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .cta {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 10px;
    }

    .primary {
      background: #60a5fa;
      color: #03111f;
    }

    .secondary {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #60a5fa;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">

    <h1>TrimWise</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
      AI-powered nutrition, workouts, and daily coaching — built to guide decisions, not just track them.
    </p>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>What TrimWise Does</h2>

      <ul class="features">
        <li>• AI coach that adapts to your goals and progress</li>
        <li>• Barcode + AI meal scanning</li>
        <li>• Smart calorie and macro targets</li>
        <li>• 7-day nutrition and workout planning</li>
        <li>• Real-time decision support for food and training</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <a class="button primary" href="#">
        Download Coming Soon
      </a>

      <a class="button secondary" href="./privacy.html">
        Privacy Policy
      </a>

      <a class="button secondary" href="./terms.html">
        Terms of Use
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 TrimWise  
      <br/><br/>
      <a href="./privacy.html">Privacy</a> |
      <a href="./terms.html">Terms</a>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
